<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>Imgur Gallery</title><link>https://imgur.com</link><description>description</description><lastBuildDate>2022-06-13 15:29:26.926475</lastBuildDate><item><title>In honour of Pride Month, here's my rollercoaster of a weekend</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/CZGoumn</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/sbdhwso.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/J0y5Npc.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/YmhCNGU.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/FYmXoLi.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/a8MhFEb.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Dp3wl24.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/SsNfnm5.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/JBivg7N.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/XvopZtS.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/PHbfGeJ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I'm so happy and can't stop smiling! Don't know how I'm going to get anything done in the next few days, all I'm thinking about is her. Can't wait for Wednesday!!!!

After being married to a man for 9 years, divorce, losing my job, and a bunch of other shit last year, I feel like I haven't felt in years. It also helps that she is drop dead gorgeous, and I can't believe she thinks the same about me! How anyone can look like an angel while hungover is beyond me.

With a few girls I tried dating or just hooked up with, I felt like they were afraid or ashamed (of me or themselves, idk). This one kissed me in the street, held my hand, kissed me goodbye at the bus stop, didn't want to let go. We live in a pretty homophobic country, so she was so brave and made me feel safe to do that. She's just amazing, I don't know what else to say!

EDIT: After five years on Imgur, my first post to reach MV! Send memes to send to her I guess? No nudes please :)</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/CZGoumn</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[jelisaveta]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Danish girls sing to Obama</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/Eg2zbOr</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/kVLJGD1.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Eg2zbOr</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[darryljenks]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Wholesome as heck</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/KmJZMNa</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/TzSxhfe.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>*Front page edit*

