an ahead of his time, with a very admirable concern for man's best friend. Dogs are family ❤</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/yE52mQa</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[mfrybeasley]]></dc:creator></item></channel></rss>